{"tid":710303,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[15號苦主]我張15號既演唱會飛尾貼起佢","createTime":"2018-06-20T15:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T15:43:52.000Z","uid":60123,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d8eb21fd4dce5fe46586afda00356ebb0badb6","tid":710303,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"記得李嘉誠將AIG股票裱起 黎警惕自己買賣股票既風險<br />\n我都效法超人 將6月15號飛尾貼起 提醒自己當日係點撚樣打電話打到痴左線去撲佢既飛 而佢最後點樣撚狗我地呢d歌迷<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以此為鑑</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/233043_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F233043_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0ef977e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完左場show仲要唔係解釋番點解當日提早收檔 而係鬧歌迷俾左錢就當自己係老闆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢依家就同大家證明佢先係老闆 佢特別憎15號 就撚狗你地班契弟 <br />\n張敬軒：係呀 撚狗你地呀 吹呀？你買我演唱會飛 就係入黎俾我撚架啦 我先係你地老闆 成堆傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0417f41d761d367db7814c2524db224b4003df","tid":710303,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:40:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d140cd3e1b4197239c18b9e331204d73683632ba","tid":710303,"uid":7175,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:43:52.000Z","msg":"唔好咁肉酸啦"}]}